            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">8.1104</ph> Contract clauses.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p class="- topic/p ">Insert the following clauses in solicitations and contracts for leasing of motor vehicles, unless the motor vehicles are leased in foreign countries:</p>
			      <ol id="d521e16" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d529e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1062379.dita#i1062379"
                        base="i1062379"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-4</xref>, Vehicle Lease Payments.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d529e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1062392.dita#i1062392"
                        base="i1062392"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-5</xref>, Condition of Leased Vehicles.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d529e44" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1062403.dita#i1062403"
                        base="i1062403"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-6</xref>, Marking of Leased Vehicles.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d529e56" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            A clause substantially the same as the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1062413.dita#i1062413"
                        base="i1062413"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-7</xref>, Tagging of Leased Vehicles, for vehicles leased over 60 days <ph class="- topic/ph ">(see subpart B of 41 CFR part 102-34)</ph>.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d529e71" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The provisions and clauses prescribed elsewhere in the FAR for solicitations and contracts for supplies when a fixed-price contract is contemplated, but excluding-</p>
					          <ol id="d521e74" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d529e81" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1063103.dita#i1063103"
                              base="i1063103"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.211-16</xref>, Variation in Quantity;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d529e93" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1049385.dita#i1049385"
                              base="i1049385"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.232-1</xref>, Payments;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d529e105" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055699.dita#i1055699"
                              base="i1055699"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.222-20</xref>, Contracts for Materials, Supplies, Articles, and Equipment Exceeding $15,000; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d529e117" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1047139.dita#i1047139"
                              base="i1047139"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.246-16</xref>, Responsibility for Supplies.</p>
							              <p id="d529e126" class="- topic/p "/>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
